review_blob: I drink this stuff...when Im drunk and short of cash!  For the well informed, this is a very basic drink. It looks like a beer, smells like a beer, and tastes like a beer. At the Barbie, its a great companion with the tucker. Pour it cold into a glass...never drink out of the can. Stubbies excepted.  Overall a nice drop on a hot day and as the ad says "a hard earned thirst..." fits in well in our wide...dry...hot...brown land.
